{
  "name": "mimic-tcp-udp-fallback",
  "doc": "Two routers joined by a transport=tcp (mimic) link whose mimic_fallback=udp. Pins the install.sh policy=udp branch: a mimic provisioning failure sets _MIMIC_SKIP=1 and the link comes up as plain UDP (the _mimic_provision fail-degradable path), NOT the fail-closed exit the mimic-tcp fixture pins. No catalog is configured here (the contract harness has no Fetch field), so the two-package .mimic.debs[k] dkms_asset/dkms_sha256 JSON shape is pinned separately by internal/render/artifacts_json_test.go.",
  "custody": "airgap",
  "signing": false,
